# Project Context

- Playwright bot: monitors Instagram targets, generates Gemini comments, posts them
- Educational use only — automating Instagram violates ToS; account ban risk
- TypeScript in `src/`; config in `src/config.ts`; runtime data in `data/`
- npm scripts: `start` (monitor), `test` (test-comment), `checker` (check-accounts)
- Modes via CLI: `npx ts-node src/main.ts [monitor|test-comment|check-accounts]`
- Controls: CTRL+C to stop; `i` key requests Playwright Inspector pause
- Match existing patterns: class-based modules, chalk `Logger`, async/await
